channel.description: Backstory on this thing - I made a track titled ‘Miami’ which was my first proper song on Auxy at around March 2018, and decided to remix it twice (VIP in around May, and VIP VIP around August) it was basically to show that I’ve kinda improved so to say, but - enjoy ! https://soundcloud.com/krisw5821/sets/big-fat-evolution
